title: Episode 134 | "Frock-a-fella"
description: Joe, Rory and Mal finally had the chance to discuss Eminem’s freestyle (2:26). Miko Grimes joins to give her thoughts on being friends with ex’s, an update on Taxstone and how she finessed the NFL (1:14:59). Also, Tyrese is at it again and the guys talk about his latest drama on Instagram (31:05). This episode is for V.I.P’s only. Other topics include.. - Lil B getting jumped by A Boogie’s camp (11:22) - This Is Us [TV show] (24:04) - Get well soon Combat Jack (28:10) - Strippers going on strike (1:03:10 - Mal wishes Drake a happy birthday (1:12:53) Sleeper Songs: Joe: H.E.R.
